Subject: [PATCH] Secret management (#2)

* SECURITY-1514 Use secret correctly
---
 build.gradle                                  | 18 +++++++-------
 server.bat                                    |  2 --
 .../proget/jenkins/ProGetConfiguration.java   | 15 ++++++------
 .../com/inedo/proget/api/ProGetApiTests.java  |  2 +-
